'''Abia State''' bu state no n'ime [[Naigeria]]. Isị ya bu [[Umuahia]], tomadi [[Aba]] bu ebe ahia ukwu ya no. Abia State nola n'afo [[Imo State]] ru [[1991]], mgbe ndi government coro ya guzie ya state. [[Ndi Igbo]] bi na ya na nke ukwu. Obu otu state n'iteghete meka ebe ana-kpo ''Niger Delta''.


